```plantuml
@startuml jinnerbichler_flash-home

actor User

participant "Home Assistant" as HA
participant "Coffee Machine Client" as CMClient
participant "Flash Server (Coffee Machine)" as FSCoffee
participant "Flash Server (Provider)" as FSProvider
participant "Private IOTA Testnet" as IOTATestnet

User -> HA: Make Coffee Request
HA -> CMClient: Trigger Coffee Brew
CMClient -> FSCoffee: Initialize Flash Channel
FSCoffee -> FSProvider: Request Channel Initialization
FSProvider -> FSCoffee: Confirm Channel Initialization
FSCoffee -> CMClient: Channel Initialized

CMClient -> FSCoffee: Sign Transaction
FSCoffee -> FSProvider: Forward Signed Transaction
FSProvider -> FSCoffee: Transaction Confirmed
FSCoffee -> CMClient: Transaction Completed

CMClient -> IOTATestnet: Broadcast Transaction
IOTATestnet -> CMClient: Transaction Successful

CMClient -> HA: Update Coffee Brew Status
HA -> User: Display Brew Status

@enduml
```